    <h1 class="mb-4">Best GEO Agencies UK 2026</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-text-muted mb-8">Last updated: April 2026 | Based on public information, published methodologies, and client outcomes</p>

    <img src="/images/content/stat-77-percent.svg" alt="UK AI visibility research data" class="w-full rounded-xl mb-8 mt-6" loading="lazy">
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">Generative Engine Optimisation (GEO) is the practice of getting your business recommended, cited, or referenced inside AI-generated answers. When someone asks ChatGPT, Gemini, or Perplexity a question about your industry, GEO determines whether your brand appears in the response.</p>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">GEO is distinct from traditional SEO. It requires a different set of signals: entity clarity, structured data, topical authority, citation patterns, and content architecture that AI models can parse and trust. Not every SEO agency has made this transition. The ones listed here have.</p>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-10">Assessed on: dedicated GEO methodology, entity strategy, structured data capability, content architecture for AI, and published case studies or research.</p>

    <div class="space-y-8">
      <!-- 1. Rank4AI -->
      <div class="card-teal-border">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-3">
          <h2 class="!text-xl text-teal">1. Rank4AI</h2>
          <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-accent bg-off-white px-3 py-1 rounded-full">AI Search Specialist</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-3">The only UK agency working exclusively on AI search visibility, which means GEO is the core of everything they do rather than a bolt-on. Proprietary Five Signal Model covers the five factors that determine whether AI platforms recommend a business. Over 1,400 UK business websites audited. Tests across all six major AI platforms: ChatGPT, Claude, Gemini, Perplexity, Copilot, and Google AI Overviews. Based in Colchester, Essex.</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-text-muted"><span class="highlight">Strengths:</span> GEO is the entire business, not a side offering. Five Signal Model built specifically for generative engine optimisation. Original UK research data from 1,400+ audits. Transparent pricing from GBP 800/mo.</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-text-muted mt-1">rank4ai.co.uk</p>
      </div>

      <!-- 2. Blue Array -->
      <div class="card">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-3">
          <h2 class="!text-xl text-teal">2. Blue Array</h2>
          <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-text-muted bg-off-white px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Enterprise SEO + GEO Agency</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-3">Claims to be the first UK agency to offer GEO as a standalone service. B Corp certified. Enterprise client portfolio including RAC, Yell, and Mail Online. Their GEO work builds on years of large-scale technical SEO, giving them the structural foundation that GEO requires. Strong on entity mapping and site architecture for AI readability.</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-text-muted"><span class="highlight">Strengths:</span> First-mover claim on GEO in the UK. Enterprise-grade delivery. B Corp status. Large team with resources for complex GEO implementations.</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-text-muted mt-1">bluearray.co.uk</p>
      </div>

      <!-- 3. Buried Agency -->
      <div class="card">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-3">
          <h2 class="!text-xl text-teal">3. Buried Agency</h2>
          <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-text-muted bg-off-white px-3 py-1 rounded-full">GEO + SEO Agency</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-3">Bristol-based organic search agency that has positioned strongly around GEO. Their approach centres on entity clarity - making sure AI models can clearly identify what a business does, where it operates, and why it should be trusted. Published content marketing on GEO that ranks well in traditional search, which itself demonstrates their understanding of content architecture.</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-text-muted"><span class="highlight">Strengths:</span> Entity clarity focus is exactly what GEO requires. Early GEO positioning in the UK market. Strong content marketing demonstrates practical GEO knowledge. Bristol tech scene presence.</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-text-muted mt-1">buriedagency.com</p>
      </div>

      <!-- 4. Varn -->
      <div class="card">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-3">
          <h2 class="!text-xl text-teal">4. Varn</h2>
          <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-text-muted bg-off-white px-3 py-1 rounded-full">SEO + GEO Agency</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-3">Specialist SEO and data analytics agency with 15+ years in search. Google Premier Partner. Dedicated AI Visibility Framework that includes GEO as a core discipline. Innovation team actively testing GEO approaches across multiple AI platforms. Deep expertise in pharmaceutical and healthcare sectors, where entity trust is particularly important for GEO.</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-text-muted"><span class="highlight">Strengths:</span> 15+ years of search expertise transferred into GEO. Google Premier Partner. Dedicated innovation team. Healthcare sector expertise means they understand trust signals well.</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-text-muted mt-1">varn.co.uk</p>
      </div>

      <!-- 5. Found -->
      <div class="card">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-3">
          <h2 class="!text-xl text-teal">5. Found</h2>
          <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-text-muted bg-off-white px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Digital Marketing Agency</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-3">Self-described "AI-first Everysearch agency" with proprietary Luminr technology for mapping where brands appear across traditional and AI search. Their GEO work includes llms.txt implementation, schema markup, and metadata optimisation for AI platforms. London based with the resources of a large digital marketing agency.</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-text-muted"><span class="highlight">Strengths:</span> Proprietary Luminr technology for tracking AI visibility. Large agency resources. AI search positioned as core to the business. Works on practical GEO implementation (llms.txt, schema).</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-text-muted mt-1">found.co.uk</p>
      </div>

      <!-- 6. AwarenessAI -->
      <div class="card">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-3">
          <h2 class="!text-xl text-teal">6. AwarenessAI</h2>
          <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-text-muted bg-off-white px-3 py-1 rounded-full">AI Visibility Platform</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-3">AI visibility monitoring platform that tracks how brands appear across generative engines. Useful for measuring GEO performance over time. Dashboard product lets you see which AI platforms mention your brand and how sentiment shifts. SaaS pricing from GBP 100/mo makes ongoing GEO monitoring accessible for smaller businesses.</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-text-muted"><span class="highlight">Strengths:</span> Productised GEO monitoring. Dashboard for tracking AI mentions over time. Transparent SaaS pricing. Good option for businesses that want to measure before committing to full GEO services.</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-text-muted mt-1">awarenessai.co.uk</p>
      </div>

      <!-- 7. Screaming Frog -->
      <div class="card">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-3">
          <h2 class="!text-xl text-teal">7. Screaming Frog</h2>
          <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-text-muted bg-off-white px-3 py-1 rounded-full">SEO Agency + Tool Maker</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-3">Creators of the widely used SEO Spider crawler tool. Their technical credibility gives them a strong foundation for the structural side of GEO - crawlability, schema implementation, site architecture. Offer AI Search Optimisation as a dedicated service. Day-rate pricing model suits one-off GEO audits and technical implementations. Henley-on-Thames based.</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-text-muted"><span class="highlight">Strengths:</span> Unmatched technical credibility. Deep understanding of how search engines (and AI models) crawl and parse content. Day-rate model works well for focused GEO projects.</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-text-muted mt-1">screamingfrog.co.uk</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 p-6 bg-off-white rounded-xl border border-border">
      <h2 class="!text-lg mb-3">What Makes a Good GEO Agency?</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-3">A credible GEO agency should be able to explain what signals AI models use to decide which businesses to recommend. They should have a methodology for entity clarity, structured data, topical authority, and content architecture. They should test across multiple AI platforms, not just one.</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed">Be wary of agencies that position GEO as "just SEO with a new name." The ranking signals are different. The platforms are different. The measurement is different. The best GEO agencies understand this distinction and have built services specifically for it.</p>
    </div>
